text: Rogówek may refer to the following places in Poland: *Rogówek, Kłodzko County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Rogówek, Wołów County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Rogówek, Podlaskie Voivodeship (north-east Poland) *Rogówek, Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship (south-central Poland) *Rogówek, Masovian Voivodeship (east-central Poland)
title: Rogówek
